				<a name="31"></a>
				<FONT COLOR="4a0000"><B>Today's Dev Quotes</B></FONT><BR>
				<TABLE border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="1"><TR>
				<TD bgcolor="#aaaaaa"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="-2"><a href="responses.cfm?id=31">Add Comment</A> (1)</font> &nbsp; &nbsp;</TD>
				<TD bgcolor="#aaaaaa"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="-2"><a href="archive.cfm?month=4&year=2000&week=4&category_id=4" title="View news of this category"><font color="ca0000">Dev Quotes</font></a></font> &nbsp; &nbsp; </TD>
				<TD bgcolor="#aaaaaa"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="-2">Server: N/A</font>&nbsp;</TD>
				<TD bgcolor="#aaaaaa"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="-2">Posted By: <A HREF="mailto:louise.hand@virgin.net">Carramaena</A></font> &nbsp; &nbsp; </TD>
				<TD bgcolor="#aaaaaa"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="-2">05:22 PM</font>&nbsp;</TD>
				</TR></TABLE>
				<p>On the forums today, Abashi discusses the lack of music in Kunark zones, rejects the idea of allowing the Priest of Discord to bind characters in cities and responds to another player conserned about losing their corpse in Veeshan's Peak. He also explains why the Veeshan server seemed to have the same number of players after the split as before, hints at when the new Posion Update will be complete and explains why binding isn't allowed at the Fire Pots.</p>
<p>For the full posts, click this link. <a href="article.cfm?id=31"><font size="1">Read More...</font></a>
				<br><br>
				
				
			
		
			
		
			
		
			
		
			
		
			
		
			
		
			
		
